title: Example Inline Note
text: This is an example inline note that will appear as a popup when referenced using the `<<inline-note "Example Inline Note">>` macro.

You can include any content here:
- Lists
- **Bold text**
- *Italic text*
- Links
- And more!

The popup will automatically position itself and can be closed by clicking outside of it.

## Try it out

Use this macro anywhere in your wiki:
`<<inline-note "Example Inline Note">>`
